{"tid":1375811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【眾籌】點解自己有錢唔揾專業人仕做嘢？","createTime":"2019-07-28T07:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:17:54.000Z","uid":51814,"like":535,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"0670a418819711cdd796c103bf7a14505ee58e95","tid":1375811,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:00:37.000Z","msg":"如果屎坑塞咗，你會揾通渠佬。<br />\n<br />\n如果天花爛咗，你會揾裝修佬。<br />\n<br />\n如果警察黑咗，你會自己去搞？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">污糟邋遢嘢緊係揾師傅搞啦</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，我地只不過係雞蛋，但唔係普通嘅雞蛋，香港係個生金蛋嘅國際城市，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>所以我地係金蛋</strong></span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n香港人雖然冇勇氣犯法，但係非常有錢，有錢到可以養起半個中國。所以政府控制咗隻雞，先有咁多錢去自肥，尤其係警隊，集軍權政權於一身，係政府第二把交椅，一切聽命於林鄭特首？<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>完全係挾天子以令諸侯</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n普通市民要對抗佢地，即使勇武至行使暴力，亦隨時被和理非出賣，失去民意支持淪為condom。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>唔想場運動好似雨傘咁不了了之，然後繼續交税俾第二把交椅以權謀私，唯有係用錢解決</strong></span></span>。唔駛罷工，亦唔駛阻人返工，香港人一齊努力揾錢，有錢使得鬼推磨。<br />\n<br />\n要好多錢？肯定少過罷工罷市嘅損失，如果起到殺雞儆猴嘅效果，可能商家都會支持俾大份。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>你睇下老豆揾仔，幾多差佬25仔做線人賣料，就知道對家已經人人自危，有好多主謀已逃離海外，更加容易落手</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港市民會覺得好殘忍？</strong></span></span>處於道德高地嘅佢準時交税交差餉，結果黑警白衣人咁樣設局打香港人，同贊助恐怖襲擊有乜嘢分別？<br />\n<br />\n我在夢入面仲睇咗套戲，蝙蝠俠黑夜之神，劇情如有雷同，實屬巧合。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/28/134252_43c78bc75aaf9f9e59544f856a10f122.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F28%2F134252_43c78bc75aaf9f9e59544f856a10f122.gif&h=71c64d4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8e2d9fb898cc9eba786b8072d64f121220376f2","tid":1375811,"uid":45523,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:03:26.000Z","msg":"啱呀 支持！"},{"pid":"490a2fa2d9ad9dcc5ec864b6a3171a4d45c09803","tid":1375811,"uid":14494,"like":147,"dislike":1,"score":146,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"請外國僱傭兵取締特區警察維持法治<br />\n<br />\n久而久之，每次都只會係遊行示威見到黑警，就可以正式宣布黑警=維穩機器"},{"pid":"2871af90c963b078f7afef10dd525887f7652207","tid":1375811,"uid":51814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:15:11.000Z","msg":"開錯台，下次去返影視台"},{"pid":"9264f9654ff756cb6656341df12258ab982ccf67","tid":1375811,"uid":122709,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:16:00.000Z","msg":"有冇可以請到僱傭兵？應該入唔到境？"},{"pid":"38bd4bfac3eb224a3efa37fa96bb6e1733f505b8","tid":1375811,"uid":51814,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/28/152150_1cdc452a0b0951ae666f85f55ce06bc1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F28%2F152150_1cdc452a0b0951ae666f85f55ce06bc1.gif&h=bac293ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b5dc26e3c5cbe6929daa23e33c934607c876388","tid":1375811,"uid":51814,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9264f9654ff756cb6656341df12258ab982ccf67","tid":1375811,"uid":122709,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:16:00.000Z","msg":"有冇可以請到僱傭兵？應該入唔到境？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"討論返劇情，向Reese出追殺令後，係全城市民都響應，包括老婆在醫院嘅黑警"},{"pid":"630442ff361a62055d633447ca7d7726888e38b4","tid":1375811,"uid":51814,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:51:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pbpf7vJNLVw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fpbpf7vJNLVw&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=d65c65c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pbpf7vJNLVw</a><br />\n<br />\n補返段片"},{"pid":"89b41f777997cc42014ca8c5cdf74eeebde4